headline: Otis to Equip 68-storey Dawn KLCC with Elevators in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
summary: Otis (NYSE: OTIS), the world's leading elevator and escalator manufacturing, installation and service company, will install seven Otis SkyRise® and three Otis Arise™ elevators for the Chin Hin Group Property Dawn KLCC mixed-used building.
